::Battera::

She looked at Cybershark

"Uh, thanks for the use of your CR chamber."
She looked at the floor, "but I really should be going now. If you would 
please show me to the door, I'll trouble you no longer."
She had to leave, or she would start sobbing.  She felt so bad about leaving 
her frineds to die as she did.  But she knew that if she hadn't of escaped, 
she'd be dead too.  The conflict of survival or dishonor was eating her 
apart.
